# ── Uploaded files & local database ─────────────────────────────────────────
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT ignore /uploads or /data.
# These directories hold user files and the SQLite DB.
# They must be preserved on the server across deployments.
#
# If you use git to deploy, commit these directories.
# If you use rsync/scp, always sync them to the server.
#
# Only ignore metadata.json (superseded by SQLite):
/uploads/metadata.json
